{"name":"glib::optiongroup","body":"\n\n<h1 align=\"center\">Glib::OptionGroup</h1>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr>\n\n\n<h2>NAME\n<a name=\"NAME\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Glib::OptionGroup\n- group of options for command line option parsing</p>\n\n<h2>SYNOPSIS\n<a name=\"SYNOPSIS\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">my ($verbose,\n$source, $filenames) = ('', undef, []); <br>\nmy $entries = [ <br>\n{ long_name =&gt; 'verbose', <br>\nshort_name =&gt; 'v', <br>\narg_type =&gt; 'none', <br>\narg_value =&gt; \\$verbose, <br>\ndescription =&gt; 'be verbose' }, <br>\n{ long_name =&gt; 'source', <br>\nshort_name =&gt; 's', <br>\narg_type =&gt; 'string', <br>\narg_value =&gt; \\$source, <br>\ndescription =&gt; 'set the source', <br>\narg_description =&gt; 'source' }, <br>\n[ 'filenames', 'f', 'filename-array', \\$filenames ], <br>\n]; <br>\nmy $context = Glib::OptionContext-&gt;new ('- urgsify your\nlife'); <br>\n$context-&gt;add_main_entries ($entries, 'C'); <br>\n$context-&gt;parse (); <br>\n# $verbose, $source, and $filenames are now updated\naccording to the <br>\n# command line options given</p>\n\n<h2>HIERARCHY\n<a name=\"HIERARCHY\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Glib::Boxed\n<br>\n+----Glib::OptionGroup</p>\n\n<h2>METHODS\n<a name=\"METHODS\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>optioncontext\n= Glib::OptionContext-&gt;new ($parameter_string)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"40%\">\n\n\n<p>$parameter_string (string)</p></td>\n<td width=\"43%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>optiongroup\n= Glib::OptionGroup-&gt;new (key =&gt; value, ...)</b> <br>\nCreates a new option group from the given key-value pairs.\nThe valid keys are name, description, help_description, and\nentries. The first three specify strings while the last one,\nentries, specifies an array reference of option entries.\nExample:</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">my $group =\nGlib::OptionGroup-&gt;new ( <br>\nname =&gt; 'urgs', <br>\ndescription =&gt; 'Urgs Urgs Urgs', <br>\nhelp_description =&gt; 'Help with Urgs', <br>\nentries =&gt; \\@entries);</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">An option entry\nis a hash reference like this:</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">{ long_name\n=&gt; 'verbose', <br>\nshort_name =&gt; 'v', <br>\nflags =&gt; [qw/reverse hidden in-main/], <br>\narg_type =&gt; 'none', <br>\narg_value =&gt; \\$verbose, <br>\ndescription =&gt; 'verbose desc.', <br>\narg_description =&gt; 'verbose arg desc.' }</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Of those keys\nonly long_name, arg_type, and arg_value are required. So\nthis is a valid option entry too:</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">{ long_name\n=&gt; 'package-names', <br>\narg_type =&gt; 'string-array', <br>\narg_value =&gt; \\$package_names }</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">For\nconvenience, option entries can also be specified as array\nreferences containing long_name, short_name, arg_type, and\narg_value:</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">[ 'filenames',\n'f', 'filename-array', \\$filenames ]</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">If you\ndon&rsquo;t want an option to have a short name, specify\nundef for it:</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">[ 'filenames',\nundef, 'filename-array', \\$filenames ]</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>$context-&gt;add_group\n($group)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"40%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$group (Glib::OptionGroup)</p></td>\n<td width=\"43%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>$context-&gt;add_main_entries\n($entries, $translation_domain)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"83%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$entries (scalar) reference to\nan array of option entries</p></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"83%\">\n\n\n<p>$translation_domain (string)</p></td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>boolean =\n$context-&gt;get_help_enabled <br>\n$context-&gt;set_help_enabled ($help_enabled)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"35%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$help_enabled (boolean)</p></td>\n<td width=\"48%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>boolean =\n$context-&gt;get_ignore_unknown_options <br>\n$context-&gt;set_ignore_unknown_options\n($ignore_unknown)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"38%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$ignore_unknown (boolean)</p></td>\n<td width=\"45%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>optiongroup\n= $context-&gt;get_main_group <br>\n$context-&gt;set_main_group ($group)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"40%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$group (Glib::OptionGroup)</p></td>\n<td width=\"43%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>boolean =\n$context-&gt;parse</b> <br>\nThis method works directly on <i>@ARGV</i>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">May croak with\na Glib::Error in $@ on failure.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>$group-&gt;set_translate_func\n($func, $data=undef)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"21%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$func (scalar)</p></td>\n<td width=\"62%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"21%\">\n\n\n<p>$data (scalar)</p></td>\n<td width=\"62%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>$group-&gt;set_translation_domain\n($domain)</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"25%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">$domain (string)</p></td>\n<td width=\"58%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>ENUMS AND FLAGS\n<a name=\"ENUMS AND FLAGS\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>enum\nGlib::OptionArg</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&rsquo;none&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_NONE&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;string&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_STRING&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;int&rsquo; / &rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_INT&rsquo;</p></td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;callback&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_CALLBACK&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;filename&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_FILENAME&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;string-array&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_STRING_ARRAY&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;filename-array&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_FILENAME_ARRAY&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;double&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_DOUBLE&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"74%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;int64&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_ARG_INT64&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>flags\nGlib::OptionFlags</b></p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">&rsquo;hidden&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_HIDDEN&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;in-main&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_IN_MAIN&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;reverse&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_REVERSE&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;no-arg&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_NO_ARG&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;filename&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_FILENAME&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;optional-arg&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_OPTIONAL_ARG&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"1%\">\n\n\n<p>&bull;</p></td>\n<td width=\"5%\"></td>\n<td width=\"69%\">\n\n\n<p>&rsquo;noalias&rsquo; /\n&rsquo;G_OPTION_FLAG_NOALIAS&rsquo;</p> </td>\n<td width=\"14%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>SEE ALSO\n<a name=\"SEE ALSO\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Glib,\nGlib::Boxed</p>\n\n<h2>COPYRIGHT\n<a name=\"COPYRIGHT\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Copyright (C)\n2003-2011 by the gtk2-perl team.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">This software\nis licensed under the <small>LGPL.</small> See Glib for a\nfull notice.</p>\n<hr>\n","headings":["<a href=\"#NAME\">NAME</a>","<a href=\"#SYNOPSIS\">SYNOPSIS</a>","<a href=\"#HIERARCHY\">HIERARCHY</a>","<a href=\"#METHODS\">METHODS</a>","<a href=\"#ENUMS AND FLAGS\">ENUMS AND FLAGS</a>","<a href=\"#SEE ALSO\">SEE ALSO</a>","<a href=\"#COPYRIGHT\">COPYRIGHT</a>"],"level":3}